channel.title: United Mission to Nepal to be added to IATI Organisation Codelist
channel.description:
This topic serves as a heads up that within the next seven days (assuming that there are no objections), the United Mission to Nepal will be added to our IATI Organisation Identifier Codelist. For details, please see [this consultation](http://support.iatistandard.org/entries/83579245-Add-United-Mission-to-Nepal-to-IATI-Organisation-Identifier-Codelist).
Best wishes, Rory
